Circuit breaker day 22: Tom yum seafood soup for lunch.👩‍🍳
🔸️
Bought the sliced seabass from @haisiaseafood which were pretty good and the noodles were called 刷刷米粉 which I bought from Genting a few months' back. The combi worked well for me and I am belly-happy now 🥰
🔸️
